&none &kp LBKT &kp N7 &kp N8 &kp N9 &kp RBKT     &none &none &none &none &none &none
&none &kp SLASH &kp N4 &kp N5 &kp N6 &kp EQUAL     &none &kp RSHFT &kp RCTRL &kp RALT &kp RGUI &none
